<materialsCitation location="Area de Protecao Ambiental Tinhare-Boipeba" pageId="21" pageNumber="174" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Bahia">
has an EOO of 
<quantity box="[903,1023,1989,2017]" metricMagnitude="7" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.8943" pageId="21" pageNumber="174" unit="km" value="78943.0">78,943 km</quantity>
² and AOO of 
<quantity box="[1185,1308,1988,2017]" metricMagnitude="7" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" pageId="21" pageNumber="174" unit="km" value="25000.0">25,000 km</quantity>
², and should be classified as “Least Concern” (LC), following 
<bibRefCitation author="IUCN Standards and Petitions Subcommittee &amp; Cambridge, UK" box="[688,837,2024,2050]" pageId="21" pageNumber="174" refId="ref19879" refString="IUCN Standards and Petitions Subcommittee (2017) Guidelines for Using the IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria. Version 13 (March 2017). Prepared by the IUCN species survival commission. IUCN Council, Gland, Switzerland and Cambridge, UK, 108 pp. Available from: http: // cmsdocs. s 3. amazonaws. com / RedList Guidelines. pdf (Accessed 9 February 2019)" type="book" year="2017">IUCN (2017)</bibRefCitation>
categories. In 
<collectingRegion box="[1001,1069,2024,2050]" country="Brazil" name="Bahia" pageId="21" pageNumber="174">Bahia</collectingRegion>
, this species has been found in the “ 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03A0879A92457725FF76FBE1FCBDBDB7:8ED6605792457727FF6CF7DCFD0BB46E" box="[146,666,2059,2087]" name="Area de Protecao Ambiental Tinhare-Boipeba" pageId="21" pageNumber="174" stateProvince="Bahia">Área de Proteção Ambiental Tinharé-Boipeba</location>
”, but also within private properties
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
